Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:48.14,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(537,0)}WHOLE CAKE ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:50.71,Title,,0,0,250,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Aventura no bosque misterioso
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:50.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá vamos nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por mais que eu olhe, não deixa de me emocionar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:53.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu também!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Channel 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Shark Submerge 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:17.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, vou levar Pedro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:24.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu disse que iria sozinho, mas \Nacabei incomodando Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:29.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com certeza serei útil, Pedro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:30.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Minha especialidade é a infiltração!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:36.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aconteça o que acontecer, conseguirei\N uma cópia do Poneglyph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, conto com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:38.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:39.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:43.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depois que nos reencontrarmos com Sanji e Pudding, os esperaremos aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Todos devemos agir com cautela!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se esqueçam da mensagem de Pekoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.15,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,3210,3710)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.15,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,3210,3710)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.15,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,3210,3710)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.15,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,3210,3710)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.15,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,3210,3710)}Dê meia-volta.
Comment: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,TURN BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:54.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, decidimos avançar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não temos mais opção!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Contamos com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Boa sorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ânimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:03.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:43.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Profundidade: 15 metros.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:45.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Visibilidade: boa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:52.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo está bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:58.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Avancemos pelo rio e\Ncheguemos ao castelo de Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espero que o rio seja profundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:16.40,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(525,0)}COSTA SUDOESTE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viva!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, desembarcamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chegamos à ilha de Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sinto o cheiro de aventura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:36.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Assim que encontrarmos\N Sanji-kun, voltaremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:48.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viemos, como prometemos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não grite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os inimigos nos descobrirão!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:55.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, você realmente os viu, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há dúvida!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:02.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas quando olhei, eles já não estavam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami, coma o chão!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:10.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É creme batido solidificado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É merengue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que toda a ilha é de doce?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quero morar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:32.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji e Pudding estavam aqui, mas \Ndesapareceram quando desviei o olhar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:36.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há dúvida de que\N esta é a costa sudoeste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:42.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sei que você não mentiria, \Nmas não vejo por que eles iriam embora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:45.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quero ver o Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:05:59.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ali está!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.88,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:05.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.44,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Sanji estava ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que ele está se escondendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:35.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O-O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para onde ele foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Perdemos ele de vista!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas este lugar parece delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É uma floresta de doces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O cheiro é delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:58.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se os três viram, não há dúvida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:02.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas por que ele foi embora?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:08.19,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(290,0)}Confiem no que vou lhes dizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:12.20,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,492)}Não pretendia esconder nada dos meus companheiros.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Talvez ele se sinta incomodado por isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:21.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Apareça!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:24.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viemos te buscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, vamos nos separar para procurá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:39.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu vou por ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde estão os bolos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu vou direto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:45.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde cheira a caramelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, eu vou por ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que grãs de geleia tão lindas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pressinto um segundo desastre!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Perdemos ele de vista, então\N devemos seguir nossos instintos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É por isso que as pessoas se perdem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:06.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Além disso, será que não estão\N com outras coisas em mente?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Outras?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Claro que não.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mentirosos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos procurar juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:21.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se afastem de mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Essa flor é um doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:31.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é o que cheira a caramelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gruda nos meus dentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que felicidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não esqueceram, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:00.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viemos buscar o Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:03.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os doces estão distraindo demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nosso objetivo é encontrar o Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas tem comida por toda parte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não acha estranho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos em território inimigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos procurar mais um pouco, mas se não encontrarmos o Sanji, voltaremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.41,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:30.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse rio verde é suco de melão!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me dá um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se repararem, essa ponte é uma rosquinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:36.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:38.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cruzem a ponte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um crocodilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Derrotamos ele, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, humanos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você achou que éramos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso não importa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:38.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse crocodilo estava vestido e\N com um chapéu, e ainda falava!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como pensei, essa floresta é perigosa e estranha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:46.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E você ainda se surpreende com isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:51.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, você sabe o que eu quis dizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:10.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Melhor confiar na Pudding \Ne esperar na costa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com certeza ela trará o Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Além disso, olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nosso caminho de volta está em perigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos ficar bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Podemos voltar quando\N quisermos se pularmos sobre o rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,700)}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:39.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tem outro Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.13,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,700)}Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,700)}Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem sou eu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.37,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Quem sou eu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem é o Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles se movem igual e falam a mesma coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, são um pouco diferentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:12.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É como se estivesse diante de um espelho, \Nsua cicatriz e seus acessórios estão ao contrário!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:15.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Realmente parece que há um espelho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos é esse cara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,700)}Perguntaram quem é você!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,700)}Perguntaram quem é você!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,700)}Responda, maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,700)}Responda, maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ali está!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:31.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Na árvore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.11,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.28,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Afaste-se, maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.49,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Afaste-se, maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:44.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun, o que você está fazendo aí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, ele está fugindo de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Afaste-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldição!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Avancem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:02.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sigam Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,T-Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se separem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se separem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:08.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esta floresta é estranha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com certeza algo mais vai acontecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:16.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas se deixarmos Sanji ir de novo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami, você também vai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu também vou quando\Nchutar a bunda desse cara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:35.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.02,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.86,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:13.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:13.70,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:32.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:32.55,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:42.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,H-Há um homem gigantesco enterrado!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É um gigante!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês me assustaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nós é que deveríamos dizer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:53.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem fez isso com você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:54.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:58.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seu corpo está enterrado!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:02.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou enterrado aqui porque quero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:04.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu não deveria me preocupar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:08.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quero beber um pouco de suco.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:12.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me importo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:17.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper, não leve a sério!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos ficar loucos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem, esperem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele está dizendo algo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ignore, ignore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:31.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu adoro suco de maçã.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que eu tenho a ver com isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ignore, ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:39.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se forem para a esquerda, chegarão\Nàs cachoeiras de suco de maçã.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu adoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lembrem-se do que Luffy nos disse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos procurar Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:51.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é um sonho?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:54.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estão procurando alguém?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:55.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele passou por aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não leve a sério!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:06.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se me trouxerem suco de maçã, eu digo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:32.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um coelho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:05.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há árvores e crocodilos falantes,\Ne aquele coelho queria nos matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Este lugar é estranho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar para Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ainda sabemos o caminho de volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas e o Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:17.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não sabemos mais se era o verdadeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nos encontramos depois de tanto tempo e ele só ficou deitado na árvore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:24.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sem dizer nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:29.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Além disso, se fosse o verdadeiro Sanji-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,vocês acham que ele ficaria de braços\Ncruzados enquanto sofremos tanto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Concordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:34.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A bússola...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:41.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O relógio também!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:51.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo nesta floresta é estranho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês ouviram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:23.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Juntem-se...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,670,,Árvore, árvore, árvore, árvore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:30.21,OPLetreros,,0,0,290,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,430)\fad(525,0)}COSTA SUDOESTE\NO BOSQUE SEDUTOR {i feel like its too clouded with stuff here but i dont see another way of translating it, mainly because THE SEDUCING WOODS is hardsubbed, also translation used from spanish manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:30.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,670,,Bloqueiem sua saída.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:36.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flores, flores, flores...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos brincar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:43.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos brincar de matá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper, vá mais rápido.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Essa é a minha velocidade máxima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele está vindo para cá?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, ele ainda está nos perseguindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Precisamos sair desta floresta o mais rápido possível!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:58.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse coelho é muito forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas ele não é um mink!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:08.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um usuário de Akuma no Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:12.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles perceberam...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:18.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha perceberam...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De nós...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...não perceberam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tem algo estranho.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles perceberam...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...está brincando com eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De quem eles serão presas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:37.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se os transformassem em um smoothie, seriam deliciosos...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês veem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele não pode usar eletro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:11.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se separe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:12.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, senhor pássaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:15.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:22.64,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(230,365)}PIRATAS DE BIG MOM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:22.64,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(230,365)}RANDOLPH, CAVALEIRO DAS GARÇAS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:31.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sua arma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:32.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...está vindo para cá!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:51.81,Principio,,0,0,0,,Este é o Whole Cake Château, \No castelo de Big Mom. {SC 793 T2:43}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:56.19,Principio,,0,0,0,,O lago atrás é chamado Lago Aprico.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É um navio de Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Solicitamos permissão para entrar no porto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entrem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:15.42,Principio,,0,0,0,,Os subordinados de Big Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:20.21,Principio,,0,0,0,,...e aqueles que se tornarão \Nseus subordinados podem atracar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se para o impacto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:54.25,Principio,,0,0,0,,Germa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:59.84,Principio,,0,0,0,,...é o nome da única nação que viaja pelo mar e que não tem um território próprio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.12,Principio,,0,0,0,,Seus navios se movem independentemente,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:07.93,Principio,,0,0,0,,mas ocasionalmente se unem e formam um país.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:21.65,Principio,,0,0,0,,É um país governado pela família Vinsmoke, aquela que uma vez...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:24.87,Principio,,0,0,0,,...conquistou o North Blue \Ncom base em poder militar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.94,Principio,,0,0,0,,Este é o Reino Germa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:33.50,Principio,,0,0,0,,Seu exército, o Germa 66, \Nainda é temido em todo o mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:38.12,Principio,,0,0,0,,A maioria de seus cidadãos\N são homens e soldados.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:52.97,Principio,,0,0,0,,E não há um dia em que não estejam treinando.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo mais você vai ficar aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é tão frio...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...com sua irmã, que você \Nnão vê há treze anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:23.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quantas vezes tenho que te dizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:27.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já cortei todos os laços \Nfamiliares que tinha com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:32.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só uma família maluca usaria \Numa foto de tão mau gosto como decoração.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:50.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O grande incidente em que quatro reis do North Blue foram assassinados.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:52.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A Conquista das Quatro Nações.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:24:00.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O sonho do nosso pai é que Germa volte a conquistar o North Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:02.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que há de errado nisso?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:06.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É natural que os homens \Nbusquem poder e fama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.12,0:24:10.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você não aproveita \Nser parte de uma família real...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:14.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...em vez de estar nessa \Nmiserável tripulação pirata?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:16.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não enche.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:17.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Olha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:21.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Essas dez servas farão \No que você pedir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:24.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que desejar, príncipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:27.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu me apaixonei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:29.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É porque você é da família real.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.86,0:24:35.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se continuarmos enviando tropas para países em guerra, não precisaremos nos preocupar com dinheiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:38.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não precisará lutar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.57,0:24:41.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não gosta disso?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.93,0:24:49.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os Vinsmoke conquistaram nossa riqueza com força militar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.67,0:24:53.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse sangue também corre em suas veias.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.41,0:24:55.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você está dizendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.26,0:24:57.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou me casar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.21,0:25:00.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding é uma boa garota, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:04.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Comandante-chefe, para onde você está indo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.14,0:25:06.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para o quarto onde está Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.27,0:25:07.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me incomode.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.24,0:25:24.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai, o que você veio fazer aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:31.67,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,450)\fad(647,0)}REI DO REINO DE GERMA
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:31.67,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(647,0)}VINSMOKE JUDGE - COMANDANTE-CHEFE DO GERMA 66
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.67,0:25:33.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ainda está reclamando?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.47,0:25:36.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldito...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.60,0:25:43.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu filho...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.89,0:25:45.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me chame assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.69,0:25:49.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade que tenho um pai, mas não é você!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.62,0:25:56.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você fez com Yonji?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.30,0:25:58.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele é muito forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.91,0:26:01.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Simplesmente eu sou mais forte que ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.67,0:26:11.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá para fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.60,0:26:15.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Homens falam com os punhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.72,0:26:23.85,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(286,0)}O BOSQUE SEDUTOR
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.77,0:26:25.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper! {SC792 13:52:72}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.62,0:26:26.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.47,0:26:27.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esquivem!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.14,0:26:28.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.15,0:26:34.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que há tanto barulho atrás...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.18,0:26:36.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.20,0:26:38.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.20,0:26:38.24,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.24,0:26:40.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele pode servir como um marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.66,0:26:44.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, são os de antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.74,0:26:52.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o campo de doces!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.71,0:26:56.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos quase onde o Luffy está!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.51,0:26:59.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.51,0:26:59.57,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.57,0:27:01.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sai da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.57,0:27:01.57,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Sai da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.81,0:27:07.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele continua lutando!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.45,0:27:08.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.77,0:27:10.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar para a costa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.42,0:27:12.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.42,0:27:12.52,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.52,0:27:13.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.52,0:27:13.98,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.98,0:27:15.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.47,0:27:16.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Falamos depois!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.78,0:27:19.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Este bosque está cheio de armadilhas estranhas!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.86,0:27:21.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.86,0:27:21.36,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.37,0:27:25.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Alguém está nos perseguindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.00,0:27:27.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos a toda velocidade para a saída!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.71,0:27:38.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ali está o rio onde \Napareceu o crocodilo falante!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.67,0:27:42.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se não me engano, a saída está\N passando o rio de suco de melão!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.70,0:27:45.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos pular!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.43,0:27:48.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.02,0:27:51.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.90,0:27:53.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não sou esse!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.98,0:27:56.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você disse algo, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.19,0:27:57.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.36,0:28:02.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.65,0:28:05.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos correr com todas as nossas forças!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.20,0:28:06.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.20,0:28:06.33,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.21,0:28:08.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com o Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.62,0:28:13.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele fugiu de nós e não voltou!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.06,0:28:17.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tem algo estranho com ele, apesar \Nde ser idêntico ao Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.63,0:28:20.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos falar depois de\N sair do bosque, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.09,0:28:20.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.97,0:28:23.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que bom que sabemos como sair!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.63,0:28:25.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A costa está bem perto!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.68,0:28:26.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.43,0:28:31.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.18,0:28:32.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.12,0:28:33.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.23,0:28:40.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.23,0:28:40.77,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.77,0:28:42.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.77,0:28:42.61,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.61,0:28:46.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, eles voltaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.07,0:28:49.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês poderiam tirar\N o que está preso na minha cabeça...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.33,0:28:53.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nós simplesmente voltamos direto pelo mesmo caminho que viemos!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.50,0:28:56.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você está aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.36,0:28:59.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não gritem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.35,0:29:01.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês me assustam.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.30,0:29:03.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que estou aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.82,0:29:08.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas eu estive aqui o tempo todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.01,0:29:13.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês foram embora e depois voltaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.82,0:29:16.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper, vamos para a saída de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.13,0:29:17.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.81,0:29:19.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.15,0:29:21.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tirem o que está preso na minha cabeça!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.20,0:29:28.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cruzar o campo de doces...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.58,0:29:36.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Passar sobre o rio do crocodilo...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.42,0:29:42.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora sim vamos voltar para a costa!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.59,0:29:49.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês me assustaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.01,0:29:52.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que vocês vêm de novo e de novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.81,0:29:54.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.97,0:29:57.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade que o Log Pose não funciona,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.90,0:30:02.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,mas mesmo sem isso, deveríamos conseguir voltar facilmente, é um caminho simples!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.66,0:30:06.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Devemos ir direto por este caminho...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.65,0:30:10.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Devagar, devagar...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.65,0:30:10.28,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Devagar, devagar...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.48,0:30:13.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldição.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.88,0:30:15.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flores?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.88,0:30:15.25,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flores?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.25,0:30:16.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.37,0:30:18.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,As árvores e as flores estão se movendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.12,0:30:20.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um, dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.75,0:30:23.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O chão também se moveu e falou!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.17,0:30:25.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.42,0:30:27.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que são?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.08,0:30:28.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que há com este bosque?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.72,0:30:31.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nós fomos descobertos!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.97,0:30:35.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flores, flores!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.97,0:30:35.72,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flores, flores!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.72,0:30:39.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nunca houve um caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.31,0:30:43.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(529,0)}Finalmente perceberam, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.40,0:30:45.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Do quão terrível é este bosque!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.80,0:30:48.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy, o que você está fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.80,0:30:52.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Este é o Bosque Sedutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.66,0:30:53.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.45,0:30:54.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse não é o Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.42,0:31:08.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.80,0:31:10.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem sou eu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.42,0:31:18.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas estivemos juntos todo esse tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.04,0:31:23.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por mais que fujam, \Nnão conseguirão sair deste bosque!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.92,0:31:26.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nunca...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.79,0:31:29.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Até que morram!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.32,0:31:31.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.48,0:31:35.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Calma, garota!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.48,0:31:39.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Veja a cicatriz que tenho no meu rosto.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.23,0:31:41.21,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(498,0)}OITAVA FILHA DA FAMÍLIA CHARLOTTE
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.23,0:31:41.21,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(498,0)}CHARLOTTE BRÛLÉE
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.62,0:31:41.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É terrível, não é?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.21,0:31:42.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.77,0:31:43.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma árvore?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.67,0:31:44.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não sou uma árvore!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.97,0:31:47.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sou Brûlée!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.05,0:31:48.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.65,0:31:53.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma coelha e uma garota tão fofas...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.72,0:31:55.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nada mal...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.45,0:32:00.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando vejo esses rostos bonitos,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.73,0:32:05.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,fico com vontade de arranhá-los!
